---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="File Tools | Dar1an" description="本地文件智能检索与问答系统">
  <!-- 1. 项目概览 -->
  <section id="overview">
    <header class="project-header">
      <span class="project-category">Python / Desktop App / RAG</span>
      <h1 class="project-title">
        <span class="en">File Tools</span>
        <span class="cn">本地文件智能检索与问答系统</span>
      </h1>
    </header>
    <div class="project-image-full">
      <img src="https://img.dar1an.dpdns.org/Picgo/2026/03-09-02-46-33.png" alt="File Tools" />
    </div>
    <div class="project-intro">
      <p>随着本地文件数量快速增长和隐私保护需求增强，开发的一款完全离线运行的智能文件检索工具。结合快速文件索引技术和本地/在线大语言模型，实现高效的文件搜索、内容问答和个性化推荐功能。</p>
      <div class="tech-tags">
        <span>FastAPI</span>
        <span>Pywebview</span>
        <span>Tantivy</span>
        <span>HNSWLib</span>
        <span>llama-cpp-python</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. 技术架构 -->
  <section id="architecture">
    <h2 class="section-title">技术架构</h2>
    <div class="arch-content">
      <div class="arch-item">
        <h3>后端服务</h3>
        <p>FastAPI 提供 RESTful API，模块化路由设计（搜索、聊天、配置、目录管理相互独立）</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-item">
        <h3>桌面端</h3>
        <p>Pywebview 封装 Web 界面为原生窗口，避免浏览器跨域限制，体验更接近传统软件</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-item">
        <h3>检索引擎</h3>
        <p>Tantivy 负责全文检索（基于 Rust，速度快内存占用低），HNSWLib 处理向量相似度搜索</p>
      </div>
      <div class="arch-item">
        <h3>AI 能力</h3>
        <p>FastEmbed 生成文档向量，llama-cpp-python 本地加载 GGUF 模型，支持 Phi、Qwen、Llama 等</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="rag-section">
      <h3>项目架构</h3>
      <div class="arch-diagram">
        <div class="arch-layer">
          <div class="arch-box">用户界面层<br><small>Pywebview + Bootstrap</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="arch-layer">
          <div class="arch-box">API 接口层<br><small>FastAPI 模块化路由</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="arch-layer">
          <div class="arch-box">核心业务层<br><small>IndexManager / SearchEngine / RAGPipeline</small></div>
        </div>
        <div class="arch-arrow">↓</div>
        <div class="arch-layer">
          <div class="arch-box">数据存储层<br><small>Tantivy / HNSWLib / SQLite</small></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. 核心功能 -->
  <section id="features">
    <h2 class="section-title">核心功能</h2>
    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>混合检索</h3>
        <p>关键词检索（Tantivy BM25）+ 语义检索（HNSWLib），按权重融合排序</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>智能问答</h3>
        <p>RAG 流程，先检索相关文档片段，再让 LLM 生成答案，带引用溯源</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>多格式支持</h3>
        <p>PDF、Word、Excel、PPT、Markdown 等常见办公文档</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>实时监控</h3>
        <p>文件增删改自动触发索引增量更新，不用手动重建</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>设置持久化</h3>
        <p>前端设置通过 API 保存到 YAML 配置文件，重启后依然有效</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>会话管理</h3>
        <p>智能问答支持多会话历史记录，服务器端维护，刷新不丢失</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. RAG 实现 -->
  <section id="rag">
    <h2 class="section-title">RAG 实现流程</h2>
    <div class="rag-flow">
      <div class="rag-step">
        <div class="rag-step-num">1</div>
        <div class="rag-step-content">
          <h4>检索</h4>
          <p>用户提问后，先用嵌入模型转成向量，在 HNSW 索引里找 Top-K 相似文档；同时用 Tantivy 做关键词匹配。两个分数按权重（默认 6:4）融合，重排序后取最相关的片段。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rag-step">
        <div class="rag-step-num">2</div>
        <div class="rag-step-content">
          <h4>构造 Prompt</h4>
          <p>把检索到的文档片段拼进系统提示词，加上对话历史，组成完整的上下文。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="rag-step">
        <div class="rag-step-num">3</div>
        <div class="rag-step-content">
          <h4>生成</h4>
          <p>调用本地 LLM 或 API 生成回答，同时返回引用的源文档，方便用户核对。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. 使用指南 -->
  <section id="usage">
    <div class="usage-grid">
      <div class="usage-col">
        <h2 class="section-title">安装与启动</h2>
        <div class="code-block">
          <pre><code># 克隆项目
git clone https://github.com/Dry-U/File-tools.git
cd File-tools

# 安装依赖（推荐 uv）
uv sync

# 启动应用
uv run python main.py</code></pre>
        </div>
        <ul class="feature-list">
          <li>启动后自动打开桌面窗口</li>
          <li>API 服务运行在 127.0.0.1:8000</li>
          <li>支持 Windows / macOS / Linux</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="usage-col">
        <h2 class="section-title">快速配置</h2>
        <div class="code-block">
          <pre><code># config.yaml 示例
ai_model:
  enabled: true
  mode: "api"  # 或 "local"
  api:
    provider: "siliconflow"
    api_key: "your-api-key"
    model_name: "deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-V2.5"

file_scanner:
  scan_paths:
    - "C:/Users/Name/Documents"</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. GitHub 链接 -->
  <section id="github">
    <div class="github-section">
      <div class="github-content">
        <h2 class="section-title">开源项目</h2>
        <p class="github-desc">File Tools 是一个开源项目，欢迎提交 Issue 和 Pull Request！</p>
        <div class="github-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <i class="ri-github-fill"></i>
            <span>Dry-U/File-tools</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="github-link">
        <a href="https://github.com/Dry-U/File-tools" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">
          <i class="ri-github-fill"></i>
          <span>View on GitHub</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  // 使用统一的堆叠卡片模块
  import { initStackingCards } from '/src/scripts/stacking-cards.js';

  initStackingCards({
    sections: 'section',
    sectionOrder: ['overview', 'architecture', 'features', 'rag', 'usage', 'github']
  });
</script>

<style>
  /* Sticky sections matching home page */
  section {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    min-height: 100vh;
    height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100vw;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: var(--bg-color, #050505);
    box-sizing: border-box;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-scroll-content {
    padding: 80px 10% 40px 140px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    min-height: 100vh;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow-y: auto;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* Project Header */
  .project-header {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .project-category {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .project-title {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .project-title .cn {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .project-image-full {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .project-image-full img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 240px;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .project-intro p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .tech-tags span {
    padding: 6px 14px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  /* Section Title */
  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Architecture */
  .arch-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .arch-item h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .arch-item p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .rag-section {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .rag-section h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  /* Architecture Diagram */
  .arch-diagram {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .arch-layer {
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .arch-box {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px 25px;
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    min-width: 280px;
  }

  .arch-box small {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  .arch-arrow {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  /* Features Grid */
  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .feature-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .feature-card h3 {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .feature-card p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* RAG Flow */
  .rag-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .rag-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .rag-step-num {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .rag-step-content {
    flex: 1;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .rag-step-content h4 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }

  .rag-step-content p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* Usage Grid */
  .usage-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .code-block {
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    overflow-x: auto;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .code-block pre {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: 'Consolas', 'Monaco', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .feature-list {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .feature-list li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 20px;
  }

  .feature-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #4ade80;
  }

  /* GitHub Section */
  .github-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
    gap: 30px;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .github-desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 25px;
  }

  .github-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .stat-item i {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .github-link {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 18px 35px;
    background: var(--text-main);
    color: var(--bg-color);
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
  }

  .btn-primary i {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    section {
      height: auto;
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100vw;
      left: 0;
      position: relative;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .section-scroll-content {
      padding: 80px 5% 60px !important;
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 0;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .project-header {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .project-category {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .project-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    .project-title .cn {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .project-image-full {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .project-image-full img {
      max-height: 180px;
    }

    .project-intro p {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .tech-tags {
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .tech-tags span {
      padding: 5px 10px;
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .arch-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .arch-box {
      min-width: auto;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px 15px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .rag-step {
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .rag-step-num {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .rag-step-content {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .rag-step-content h4 {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .rag-step-content p {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .usage-grid,
    .github-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    .feature-card,
    .rag-section,
    .rag-step-content {
      padding: 18px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .code-block {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .code-block pre {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }
</style>
